# makeAsyncIterator()

**Instance Method**

Creates the asynchronous iterator that produces elements of this asynchronous sequence.

## Declaration

```swift
func makeAsyncIterator() -> AppExtensionIdentity.Identities.AsyncIterator
```

## Return Value

An instance of the `AsyncIterator` type used to produce elements of the asynchronous sequence.

## Iterating the Sequence

- **next()**: Asynchronously advances to the next element and returns it.
- **AppExtensionIdentity.Identities.AsyncIterator**: The type of the asynchronous iterator created by this asynchronous sequence.
- **AppExtensionIdentity.Identities.Element**: The type of element produced by this asynchronous sequence.
